room_title: Escape room "Aztec Ruins" by Escape Kings in Charlotte
review: Great summer fun in Charlotte! We did the Aztec room - very creative. We brought two adults and two 13 year olds....they loved it!! The team who works there is great too! We will be back!!

room_title: Escape room "Aztec Ruins" by Escape Kings in Charlotte
review: We just left from completing the Aztec Ruins room! Total fun! We will be back I'm sure for some more puzzling fun!

room_title: Escape room "Aztec Ruins" by Escape Kings in Charlotte
review: Had a great time escaping the Aztec room! Employees were super friendly and helpful during our game and birthday party! Highly recommended!
